{"tid":2265288,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"27工會大混戰 爭勞顧會5席","createTime":"2020-10-31T10:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T11:20:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3416cbb0ecd4b0061b006355f22fb4c7cb832e43","tid":2265288,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:08:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/ITGT2X5MEZFYNOOUMNMNILBI3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FITGT2X5MEZFYNOOUMNMNILBI3E%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak8yzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=d7c0dd43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FITGT2X5MEZFYNOOUMNMNILBI3E%2F&h=5bb6088f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/ITGT2X5MEZFYNOOUMNMNILBI3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n27工會大混戰 爭勞顧會5席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TXZ29ZKnT1E5L7gMybxZBd0h81c=/875x492/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZOYP7YSGQFBKPD36PPCBC5OJK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTXZ29ZKnT1E5L7gMybxZBd0h81c%3D%2F875x492%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZOYP7YSGQFBKPD36PPCBC5OJK4.jpg&h=bf061e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港酒店工會主席徐考澧<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】勞工顧問委員會勞方代表換屆選舉下月21日舉行，今次選舉出現大混戰，破天荒有多達27個工會代表報名，競逐五個席位。公務員總工會更爆內訌，該會連同旗下屬會合共有三名代表出選，除了爭取連任的陳耀光外，公務員總工會主席馮耀忠及屬會政府市政職工總會外務主任賴美珠也加入戰團。<br />\n<br />\n勞顧會勞方代表每兩年換屆，新一屆提名期上月28日至本月20日展開，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公務員三工會內鬥<br />\n<br />\n現屆勞方委員有三人競逐連任，包括公務員工會聯合會總幹事梁籌庭、房屋署屋宇裝備技術主任協會主席陳耀光及社工及福利人員工會主席鄧家彪。至於現屆勞聯周小松及港九工團聯合總會李國強將退下火線，分別由勞聯副主席譚金蓮及港九酒樓茶室總工會主席羅大智接棒。<br />\n<br />\n陳耀光2018年曾以公務員總工會主席身份出選，但該會今次改派現任主席馮耀忠參戰，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n由於勞顧會選舉採用全票制，一會一票，多來年被建制派把持。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有關候選人名單、已委任獲授權代表的選舉單位名冊和選舉規則及程序，可瀏覽勞工處網頁（<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/news/LAB_Election2020.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2FLAB_Election2020.htm&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak8yzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=fa4d69bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/news/LAB_Election2020.htm</a>）。勞顧會是一個三方諮詢組織，其委員包括僱員及僱主代表，負責就有關勞工事宜向勞工處處長提供意見。"},{"pid":"d39f291ced0713739f220188507140d99e95603f","tid":2265288,"uid":1673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:20:54.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}